</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,153,531]" box="[151,1436,450,472]" pageId="1" pageNumber="597">
<keyLead box="[151,1436,450,472]" pageId="1" pageNumber="597">
-. Antennal segment III sense cones long and curved (
<figureCitation box="[722,779,450,472]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–8" captionStartId="2.[151,258,1568,1590]" captionTargetBox="[151,1429,559,1539]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[151,1435,559,1539]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–8. Hoplothrips species. H. hongruiae sp. n. 1–5: (1) Head &amp; pronotum; (2) Antenna; (3) Male sternite VIII; (4) Pelta &amp; tergites II–III; (5) Prosternum &amp; mesopresternum. (6) H. fungosus prosternites. Antennal segments III–IV 7–8: (7) H. corticis; (8) H. orientalis." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3734659" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3734659/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="597">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
)..................................................... 4
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
